INDICATOR_NAME: Road sector energy consumption (% of total energy consumption)
SOURCE_NOTE: Road sector energy consumption is the total energy used in the road sector including petroleum products, natural gas, electricity, and combustible renewable and waste. Total energy consumption is the total country energy consumption.
